 closely the simulation results. We also show that\ndeterministic patterns have the potential to significantly outperform fully\nrandom selection, both in terms of raw performance and by simplifying the\nsystem design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Feb 2022 19:05:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-22"}
