analysis reveals that cyber risks are heavy-tailed, i.e., cyber risk events\nhave a higher probability to produce extreme losses than events whose severity\nfollows an exponential distribution. Furthermore, we find that the frequency\nand severity of cyber related losses exhibits a very dynamic and time varying\nnature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Feb 2022 12:58:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 01:01:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-16"}
