ow that we can capture the simulated galaxy's complex projected\nstructures and correctly infer the input small halo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Feb 2022 12:59:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2022 17:21:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-05"}
